  "slug": "one-to-zero-perfume-area-the-alphabet",
  "title": "One to Zero — Perfume Area: The Alphabet",
  "summary": "<p>Perfume Area is a fragrance review project between Sydney Shen and Laurel Schwulst. Each review is a “prose pocket world,” lyrical and written in second person, like a tour through an imagined landscape. <em>In Perfume Area: The Alphabet</em> (2024), twenty six special reviews were delicately handpicked as a fragrance grammar and discovery set. Each perfume review, A–Z, is time-sensitive, changing according to the viewer’s local time, and fully blooming in prose for a handful of hours every day.</p>\n",
